# Health & Wellness Tracker

A comprehensive health and wellness application for Android that helps you monitor your Body Mass Index (BMI), track your sleep patterns, and manage your stress levels.

## 🌟 Features

### BMI Calculator
*   Easily calculate your Body Mass Index by providing your weight and height.
*   Get instant results and see where you fall on the health spectrum (e.g., Underweight, Normal, Overweight).

### 😴 Sleep Analysis
*   **Sleep Hypnogram:** Visualize your sleep stages throughout the night.
*   Track the quality and duration of your sleep to identify patterns and areas for improvement.

### 🧘 Stress Management
*   Monitor your stress levels with intuitive charts and visualizations.
*   Identify sources of stress and develop strategies for a healthier, more balanced life.

